OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1772062279
OL,3,CMan accused of causing wife's suicide
OL,4,Cclaims he 'loved and cherished her'
OL,6,FA man accused of causing his wife to
OL,7,Ftake her own life through a "tsunami"
OL,8,Fof domestic abuse has denied the
OL,9,Fallegations and says he "loved and
OL,10,Fcherished her deeply".
OL,12,FChristopher Trybus from Swindon is
OL,13,Faccused of the manslaughter of Tarryn
OL,14,FBaird, who died of hanging in November
OL,15,F2017.
OL,17,FThe 43-year-old also faces charges at
OL,18,FWinchester Crown Court of controlling
OL,19,Fand coercive behaviour and two charges
OL,20,Fof rape.
OL,26,@oD@]OUoD@eO]qD@YOUrD@UO]
