PN,43103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1772062279
OL,3,CMan accused of causing wife's suicide
OL,4,Cclaims he 'loved and cherished her'
OL,6,FTom Little KC, prosecuting, has told
OL,7,Fthe jury that Trybus carried out a
OL,8,F"tsunami" of abuse against his wife,
OL,9,Fincluding "extensive and escalating
OL,10,Fcontrolling, coercive and manipulative
OL,11,Fbehaviour including sexual violence of
OL,12,Ftwo rapes and other sexual assaults".
OL,14,FKaty Thorne KC, defending Trybus, told
OL,15,Fthe jury that the defendant denies the
OL,16,Fallegations and said Ms Baird
OL,17,Fpresented a "facade" to health
OL,18,Fprofessionals because of her own
OL,19,Fmental health issues.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@IO]qD@KOUtD@dO]yD@MOUyD@TO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1772062279
OL,3,CMan accused of causing wife's suicide
OL,4,Cclaims he 'loved and cherished her'
OL,6,FShe said: "This without question is a
OL,7,Ftragic case, a young woman has died
OL,8,Fand she took her own life and nothing
OL,9,Fyou decide in this courtroom can alter
OL,10,Fthe grief and loss of those who loved
OL,11,Fher."
OL,13,FMs Thorne continued: "The defence
OL,14,Fposition is Christopher Trybus was
OL,15,Fnever abusive to his wife, he didn't
OL,16,Fbeat her, he didn't break her, he
OL,17,Fdidn't coerce her, control her and he
OL,18,Fdidn't cause her death.
OL,26,@nD@KOUsD@EO]uD@VOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1772062279
OL,3,CMan accused of causing wife's suicide
OL,4,Cclaims he 'loved and cherished her'
OL,6,F"On the contrary, he loved her and
OL,7,Fcherished her deeply and his case is
OL,8,Fthat without anyone's knowledge,
OL,9,FTarryn Baird was making demonstrably
OL,10,Ffalse allegations to health
OL,11,Fprofessionals.
OL,13,F"There are injuries but the defence
OL,14,Fcase is that on a number of occasions
OL,15,FTarryn Baird made allegations of
OL,16,Fviolence which were demonstrably
OL,17,Ffalse, for example, by reporting
OL,18,Finjuries to health professionals when
OL,19,FChristopher Trybus was not even in the
OL,20,Fcountry.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1772062279
OL,3,CMan accused of causing wife's suicide
OL,4,Cclaims he 'loved and cherished her'
OL,6,F"The defence case is that one obvious
OL,7,Fexample of that on November 16, he
OL,8,Fsays that he was out of the country,
OL,9,Fhaving left on 8th November and not
OL,10,Freturned until 23rd November.
OL,12,F"And yet during that period, Tarryn
OL,13,FBaird made more than one set of
OL,14,Fallegations of domestic violence and
OL,15,Ftook photographs of injuries, each of
OL,16,Fwhich she said was caused by him."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@bO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1772062279
OL,3,CMan accused of causing wife's suicide
OL,4,Cclaims he 'loved and cherished her'
OL,6,FMs Thorne told the jury they should
OL,7,Fquestion the "reliability" of Ms
OL,8,FBaird's claims and said: "You will
OL,9,Fhear that Tarryn Baird had mental
OL,10,Fhealth problems which were
OL,11,Flongstanding and the defence case is
OL,12,Fthat she was desperately seeking help
OL,13,Fand feeling she wasn't receiving it
OL,14,Fand she may have become addicted to
OL,15,Fthe attention that her allegations
OL,16,Fbrought.
OL,26,@oD@NOUoD@ZO]pD@ZOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1772062279
OL,3,CMan accused of causing wife's suicide
OL,4,Cclaims he 'loved and cherished her'
OL,6,F"The defence case is that the reason
OL,7,Fwhy she never made the allegations to
OL,8,Fthe police or went to a refuge was
OL,9,Fbecause the allegations weren't true
OL,10,Fand she didn't want that fact to be
OL,11,Fexposed."
OL,13,FMs Thorne said Trybus denied sexual
OL,14,Fassaults against Ms Baird and added:
OL,15,F"Theirs was a healthy, consensual
OL,16,Fmarital sex life enjoyed by both of
OL,17,Fthem.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@IO]wD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
