FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1772062279
OL,3,CMan accused of causing wife's suicide
OL,4,Cclaims he 'loved and cherished her'
OL,6,F"It included some practices which may
OL,7,Fnot be familiar or comfortable to
OL,8,Feveryone, including bondage and rough
OL,9,Fsex.
OL,11,F"What goes on in other people's
OL,12,Fbedrooms can be surprising, the
OL,13,Fdefence case is that it was
OL,14,Fconsensual."
OL,16,FShe added that an injury presented by
OL,17,FMs Baird to her neck was caused by a
OL,18,F"collar" worn during sex and an audio
OL,19,Frecording from her phone was of a
OL,20,F"kinky bondage type sex" that was
OL,21,Fconsensual.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUvD@LO]zD@AOUzD@HO]|D@AOU|D@
OL,26,AXO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
