OL,3,CMan accused of causing wife's suicide
OL,4,Cclaims he 'loved and cherished her'
OL,6,FMs Thorne continued: "The allegations
OL,7,Fof Terryn Baird being trapped and
OL,8,Fcontrolled, the defence says are
OL,9,Funtrue and the defence will suggest
OL,10,Fthat they will turn out to be just
OL,11,Ffalse.
OL,13,F"You will need to consider her claims
OL,14,Fthat she was being financially
OL,15,Fcontrolled or kept away from family
OL,16,Fand friends bears scrutiny, his case
OL,17,Fis the absolute opposite is true."
OL,26,@nD@VOUuD@AOUyD@bO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
