SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1772062279
OL,3,CMan accused of causing wife's suicide
OL,4,Cclaims he 'loved and cherished her'
OL,6,FShe added: "Health professionals were
OL,7,Fbeing told a false story and her
OL,8,Fboredom and troubled mind was leading
OL,9,Fher to make allegations to seek care
OL,10,Fand attention."
OL,12,FMs Thorne said that the jury would
OL,13,Fneed to consider if Ms Baird's suicide
OL,14,Fwas a "cry for help that went
OL,15,Ftragically wrong".
OL,26,@nD@LOUrD@OO]vD@GOUwD@QO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
