PN,43112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1772062279
OL,3,CMan accused of causing wife's suicide
OL,4,Cclaims he 'loved and cherished her'
OL,6,FShe added that Trybus's actions were
OL,7,Fnot a cause of Ms Baird's suicide and
OL,8,Fsaid: "The defence case is that there
OL,9,Fare other matters such as her mental
OL,10,Fhealth difficulties and withdrawal of
OL,11,Fservices from her which led her to
OL,12,Ftake her own life."
OL,14,FTrybus, who is a software consultant
OL,15,Fand developer, denies the charges and
OL,16,Fthe trial continues.
OL,26,@pD@GOUtD@SO]
